review: Thank God, my daughter chose Example and associate. She is in very capable hands. And we appreciate the amount of hard-working being done on her behalf. I am recommended all my friends and family to use them if they ever get hit in a car. We love the fact that we get to deal directly with Aaron and not a receptionist. He is very professional and willing to go in extra mile if you ask.
